                 p.clock__message.
                   I don't know if we should be here. <br />
                   <a href="/">Stephen</a>'s gone. <br />
                   I don't know where.
         .clock__division
           if corruption == 4
             time.clock__time #{moment('02/24/1989').format('MMMDD/YY')} - #{moment(new Date()).format('MMMDD/YY')}
             time.clock__time.js_clock__digits ĮばËそoい丫
